<s> A sibling is a node with the same parent.  </s>
<s> If you have the document a b/ c/ /a , b and c both have a as their parent.  </s>
<s> b is c's previous sibling, and c is b's next sibling.  </s>
<s> If you then issue the operation a.insertbefore(d,null), or a.appendChild(d), d will become a's last child: a b/ c/ d/ /a .  </s>
